                                                                            of applicant’s expenses in Ukraine, a return/transit ticket etc).
- One of the following:
Visa for another country (if required) and tickets;
or
Document(s) confirming that passengers/cargo are to transit through Ukraine by car/coach;
or
International carrier license issued by the relevant authority of a foreign state;
Please note that applicants might be asked for additional documents by Ukraine’s visa officers (e.g. return flight tickets and other documents confirming applicants’ circumstances (to
                                                                        be defined by Ukraine’s visa officers of the relevant Embassy/Consulate General).
